column5: Hello fellow fishermen and fisherwomen. Im new to this forum and just wanted to say Hi to you all. Im not what you would call an avid fishermen. (meaning i don't get out much) but dont take that literally. I do however frequent Algonquin Park on a yearly basis. Anyway , Hello......
Good day. Best of luck on the water.
welcome aboard  lots of people on this site are not what you would call avid, but they all enjoy being here so pull up a chair
Welcome aboard, this is a nice place to hang out when not out fishing on the water!!!
Welcome and hello Blainer !   Good to see another APP on the board. It's a good place to trip and fish, if you don't mind putting a few portages behind you.
Welcome! I'm guessing you saw Terry's avatar and it made you sign up?

Welcome Blainer! I'm quite new here myself and and am completely new to fishing. I am learning so much from the awesome group here! The Salt of the Earth hang out here. Everyone here are beyond helpful and the humour is plentiful!  A HUGE word of warning...this place is extremely addictive causing less productivity!  Consider yourself warned!!!
Welcome, your gonna like it here
Its  a no Blainer , you did come to the right place ..lol . Welcome from this newbbie over here .
Welcome...fairly new myself and enjoying every minute of it.  I'm sure you will too! Bill
